dct_title_s: Map of portions of Chippewa, Clark and Eau Claire Counties, Wisconsin
dct_description_sm: Shows locations of settlers, school houses, creameries, and cheese factories; also shows Soo Line railroad.; "Lands colored red are offered for sale by the Soo Line subject to withdrawal from the market, change of price, or sale to others without notice and under conditions governing the sale of Soo Line lands. For particular information concerning these lands with reference to price, terms, etc. address W.H. Killen, Land and Industrial Commissioner, Soo Line, First National - Soo Line Bldg., Minneapolis, Minn."; Soo Line logo in upper left and upper right margins of map.; Written in pencil on University Libraries' copy: "17 My 17 g. Minn Dept. Immigration".; Stamped on University Libraries' copy: "May 17 1917".
23 x 35 Centimeters, on sheet 34 x 41 Centimeters
dct_publisher_sm: Minneapolis, St. Paul and Sault Ste. Marie Railway Co (Minneapolis, Minn)
